    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a writer who is too lazy to work on his books. Your path will be difficult: endless rejections, small payments, competition with other authors. It's no wonder that your desire to create becomes less and less every day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But perhaps happiness and success await you at the very end?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get motivated:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/2c1e6acbfa769a8eb42471b34c54e561.poster.avif?t=1771552828\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/2c1e6acbfa769a8eb42471b34c54e561.webm?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/2c1e6acbfa769a8eb42471b34c54e561.mp4?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Writing books empties your motivation scale. Do side activities to fill it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Moreover, each trial requires its own approach to replenish your motivation points. Do you have enough spirit to reach the end?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Write books in your own style:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/b78ad8f9a5c8ffedbf7c522d59724b6f.poster.avif?t=1771552828\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/b78ad8f9a5c8ffedbf7c522d59724b6f.webm?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/b78ad8f9a5c8ffedbf7c522d59724b6f.mp4?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The following genres are available for writing books: </strong> crime novel, detective, horror, fantasy, adventure, sci-fi. Choose the genre of your book and start creating! Atmosphere, protagonist character, setting and much more – <strong>only you determine what your story will be</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wise mentors and true friends:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/15443daefea7f79fe7614baad75800fe.poster.avif?t=1771552828\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/15443daefea7f79fe7614baad75800fe.webm?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/15443daefea7f79fe7614baad75800fe.mp4?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each friend has a carefully developed storyline. And you can witness all of them! Take part in the investigation of a series of murders, go on a dangerous foray into a creepy dungeon – in <strong>Lazy Writer</strong> you can find a story you'll like!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harsh world:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/c05e189048c9e94ba8c2133152a4d70a.poster.avif?t=1771552828\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/c05e189048c9e94ba8c2133152a4d70a.webm?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deep plot awaits you, filled with unexpected twists and terrifying villains. Every day, more and more sinister eyes look at you, waiting for your failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/afe0e85f2a32ba92af855197a6254c22.poster.avif?t=1771552828\" width=596 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150530/extras/afe0e85f2a32ba92af855197a6254c22.webm?t=1771552828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
